{"tid":1475073,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（緊急）求關注 林奠修改中文科口試！無廣東話了！","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:51:11.000Z","uid":286964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad973842fe158c2b45a21523b1832ac9ac66c95e","tid":1475073,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:07:37.000Z","msg":"當大家仲向到嘈緊逃犯條例時，林鄭已經修改緊中文科課程，唔洗聽同講廣東話了。<br />\n<br />\n16/9諮詢期就過啦，之後拿拿聲上立法會一讀二讀三讀搞點。DQ埋d阻頭阻勢既議員。香港人你慢慢嘈逃犯條例啦，日日食催淚彈啦。<br />\n<br />\n#滅一個文化先滅佢既語言<br />\n#咁既政府管理香港，如果無左示威者，後果會係點？<br />\n#示威者既暴力係唔岩，但哩個政府真係無得救。<br />\n#你可以唔支持黃絲，但有一日香港失去核心價值時，唔好問點解。<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcurriculum-development%2Fkla%2Fchi-edu%2Fwhats-new.html&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=c0ac2b48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/curriculum-development/kla/chi-edu/whats-new.html</a><br />\n<br />\n16/9終止諮詢的是：<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Fattachment%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation%2FTF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbg2XOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=4ce0480e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/attachment/tc/about-edb/press/consultation/TF_CurriculumReview_Consultation_c.pdf</a><br />\n&gt;Point 3.3.2, iii(P.16)<br />\n<br />\n2002 年的《中國語文教育學習領域 《中國語文教育學習領域課程指引》中指出「用普通話教中 「用普通話教中<br />\r\n文」為遠程目標。是次修訂，教育局有何建議 ，教育局有何建議？<br />\r\n現時不少學者和學校對於以普通話教授中國語文（「普教中」）仍持有不<br />\r\n同意見。由於「普教中」的成效受很多因素影響，包括教師運用普通話<br />\r\n的能力、學校的語言環境，以及學生的社交圈子等，因此，建議學校可<br />\r\n因應校情，包括教師的資歷、學生的水平、校園的語境、課程的編排、<br />\r\n教學的支援等因素，考慮是否用普通話教授中國語文，或採用何種方式用（普教中）"},{"pid":"1e27627f86231da826170718ff67c8959d7a70b8","tid":1475073,"uid":17554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:08:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b8d43a5e808d9d3d55cc53caa230c3009d05d25","tid":1475073,"uid":123936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"頂，冇人理，廣東話冇喇！推！"},{"pid":"f35d8039274b866ee9f161610a2a86463ec8593e","tid":1475073,"uid":85769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5f58a1c6bab0658107f598abd402b611d0a178","tid":1475073,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"317938d9519e0dce030b7414b95d802ec824b2b5","tid":1475073,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:09:54.000Z","msg":"好大鑊, 大陸人更容易搶我地下一代d 人既飯碗,要比藍絲知道政府圖謀"},{"pid":"4106badf473de5d3895654e7eeff09570bb2cd8c","tid":1475073,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T03:51:11.000Z","msg":"堆"}]}